      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight! I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for total perfection and that 'new car' smell, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
