    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically flawless E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned VANOS system. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and internal integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile mechanical engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Finished in a stunning factory coat with zero clear-coat failure, the car sits on a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 49200.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
